1
00:00:01,120 --> 00:00:03,850
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,850 --> 00:00:07,180
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,180 --> 00:00:09,220
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:11,030 --> 00:00:13,640
Previously on Fairy Tail!

5
00:00:13,640 --> 00:00:18,660
We managed to stop the Magic Giant, 
but our guild's been destroyed!

6
00:00:18,660 --> 00:00:23,370
During it all, Master Jose 
has come to attack Erza!

7
00:00:23,370 --> 00:00:29,740
And the battle between Natsu and Gajeel 
is now reaching its conclusion!

8
00:00:49,220 --> 00:00:53,630
It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.

9
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:58,700
I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.

10
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:01,050
The intersection of all people

11
00:01:01,050 --> 00:01:03,660
whose dreams have come true is one point:

12
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:08,290
Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!

13
00:01:08,290 --> 00:01:13,470
When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,

14
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:15,620
grasp this hand, try to take a chance.

15
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:18,890
Because you're not alone anymore, got it?

16
00:01:22,010 --> 00:01:24,000
Go forward, more and more!

17
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,520
Don't give up on your awesome dream!

18
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,780
That's right, don't cry!

19
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:29,250
Move on, my way!

20
00:01:29,250 --> 00:01:31,630
Now, with the light shining down upon you.

21
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:33,710
Don't even think about something like giving up!

22
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:36,140
Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.

23
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:41,630
Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,

24
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:45,910
can surely see the light!

25
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,050
Look!

26
00:02:03,050 --> 00:02:04,970
Our guild!

27
00:02:04,970 --> 00:02:07,450
Somebody do something!

28
00:02:07,450 --> 00:02:08,690
Damn it all!

29
00:02:08,690 --> 00:02:10,820
The shades are still coming!

30
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:13,360
That's right... Even if our 
guild's been destroyed...

31
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,850
Our fight isn't over yet!

32
00:02:15,850 --> 00:02:18,040
Yeah!

33
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:23,620
Fairy Law!

34
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:28,390
I'm going to pay you back for everything!

35
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:31,630
I'll show you that picking a fight 
with Fairy Tail was a mistake!

36
00:02:35,070 --> 00:02:37,180
Who the hell do you think I am?

37
00:02:37,180 --> 00:02:38,760
You trash!

38
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,390
Hard Fist of the Iron Dragon!

39
00:02:49,010 --> 00:02:51,810
I am... the strongest...

40
00:02:51,810 --> 00:02:53,560
This is the end for you!

41
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:56,110
Blazing Fire Dragon Fist!

42
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:05,360
This is for Levy, Jet, Droy, 
Nab, Macao, Gramps, Erza...

43
00:03:05,950 --> 00:03:07,870
...and Lucy!!

44
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:16,730
And this is for destroying our guild!

45
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:25,640
Al, that light!

46
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,470
It's Natsu!

47
00:03:35,070 --> 00:03:37,030
Are you kidding me?

48
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,750
Gajeel lost?

49
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:40,570
Natsu!

50
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:42,640
Natsu!

51
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,140
Natsu!

52
00:03:45,250 --> 00:03:47,430
Natsu won!

53
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:51,280
That d-damn... tra...

54
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:54,380
Now... we're even.

55
00:03:58,090 --> 00:03:59,050
Natsu!

56
00:04:05,690 --> 00:04:07,930
I can't move right now...

57
00:04:13,610 --> 00:04:14,900
Sheesh...

58
00:04:15,180 --> 00:04:18,140
You really overdo it, you know that?

59
00:04:18,140 --> 00:04:20,820
Aye! He's Natsu all right!

60
00:04:25,670 --> 00:04:28,740
But... that was kinda cool.

61
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:32,120
Damn...

62
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,710
He's on a whole 'nother level.

63
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:38,580
Is this... Is this what it means 
to be a Fairy Tail wizard?

64
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:39,530
I like it!

65
00:04:39,530 --> 00:04:40,460
What?

66
00:04:40,460 --> 00:04:42,050
Nevermind.

67
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:51,010
Our dragons have run quite amuck.

68
00:04:54,550 --> 00:04:58,760
It doesn't seem like you accounted 
for Natsu's battle strength.

69
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:03,990
He is just as powerful than I, if not moreso!

70
00:05:05,130 --> 00:05:08,920
Enough with the modesty, Titania Erza.

71
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:12,060
Your magical power is indeed amazing.

72
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:17,870
I have never met a wizard who could 
hold out against me for so long.

73
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:25,050
If you hadn't taken damage from Jupiter, 
I suspect we may have had a better match.

74
00:05:26,010 --> 00:05:35,950
I can't stand Makarov having a wizard 
this powerful in his or any other guild.

75
00:05:40,150 --> 00:05:44,990
Do you understand why I didn't 
finish Makarov off before?

76
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,510
Despair!

77
00:05:58,340 --> 00:06:01,790
It was to put him in despair!

78
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:14,650
When he wakes up and sees his beloved guild and his 
beloved guild members destroyed... How will he feel?

79
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:18,440
Crestfallen, I'm sure.

80
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:29,320
I'll destroy that man with despair and 
sadness never-ending. I will not let him rest!

81
00:06:29,740 --> 00:06:34,660
He'll suffer, and suffer, and suffer 
some more... 'Till the end of his days!

82
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,960
You villain!

83
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:42,710
Phantom Lord was always the number 1 guild.

84
00:06:43,130 --> 00:06:50,060
We had the most powerful magic, the most 
talented people, and the most money in the country.

85
00:06:50,060 --> 00:06:55,180
But in these past few years Fairy 
Tail has suddenly gotten powerful.

86
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:59,760
Erza, Laxus, Mystogan...

87
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:05,520
Those names were heard even in our city, and 
rumors of Salamander spread throughout the country.

88
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:11,420
And at some point suddenly Phantom Lord and Fairy 
Tail became the <i>two</i> signature guilds of this country.

89
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:15,760
I don't like it.

90
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:19,290
Especially when your guild 
was once crappy and weak!

91
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:20,500
Silence!

92
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:28,300
Are you saying you started this war 
all because of some petty jealousy?!

93
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,040
Jealousy?

94
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,280
Of course not!

95
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:34,720
I wanted to show everyone our superiority!

96
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:38,560
What a... What a worthless reason!

97
00:07:57,830 --> 00:08:04,270
I've long had a distaste for your guild, so 
the trigger to go to war was but a trifle.

98
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:11,440
A request to return the first 
daughter of the Heartfilia Konzern.

99
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,780
Lucy?

100
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:17,340
A daughter of one of the richest 
families in the country in Fairy Tail?

101
00:08:17,340 --> 00:08:22,130
How big must you get 
before you're satisfied?!

102
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:27,240
If you bastards can use the Heartfilia's money as you wish,

103
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:31,320
there's no mistaking that you could gain power greater than ours.

104
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:34,510
That, I cannot allow.

105
00:08:38,500 --> 00:08:42,670
Making such a big deal about 
who's on top... It's pitiful.

106
00:08:42,670 --> 00:08:47,290
But it's your lack of information 
gathering that's laughable!

107
00:08:47,290 --> 00:08:48,530
What?

108
00:08:48,530 --> 00:08:50,420
Lucy ran away from home.

109
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:52,690
You think she uses her family's money?

110
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,800
She lives in a rented house 
for 70,000 jewel a month!

111
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:59,550
She does jobs and fights, together with us!

112
00:08:59,850 --> 00:09:01,010
We laugh together...

113
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:02,770
Cry together...

114
00:09:02,770 --> 00:09:04,980
She's a wizard like any other in the guild!

115
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,080
I still want to be in the guild...

116
00:09:08,570 --> 00:09:10,870
I love Fairy Tail!

117
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:14,150
A trigger for war?

118
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:17,990
We'd rather die than sell out our friends!

119
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:21,840
The daughter of the Heartfilia family?

120
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:26,540
As a flower cannot choose the place it 
blooms, neither can a child choose their parents...

121
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:43,410
A fiend like you knows nothing of 
Lucy's tears! You can't know her!

122
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:46,310
I'll learn soon enough!

123
00:09:46,990 --> 00:09:51,850
Do you seriously think I'd just 
hand her over to her father?

124
00:09:51,850 --> 00:09:55,100
If she doesn't have any 
money, I'll keep her...

125
00:09:55,780 --> 00:10:00,530
I'll get the entire Heartfilia fortune!

126
00:10:00,830 --> 00:10:02,650
Why, you...

127
00:10:04,270 --> 00:10:06,280
Don't struggle.

128
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:08,410
It'll just cause you to suffer more.

129
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:19,140
Now, shall we start the horror show?

130
00:10:19,140 --> 00:10:23,880
Let's show how you're doing 
to the rest of Fairy Tail...

131
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,930
Titania, so full of pride...

132
00:10:25,930 --> 00:10:31,150
If they see your pitiful state, the 
rest of the trash are sure to give up!

133
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:33,470
Does your wretchedness know no bounds?

134
00:10:33,470 --> 00:10:37,240
You'll be looking pretty 
wretched yourself in a moment.

135
00:10:42,530 --> 00:10:45,400
If I'm a liability to the guild, then...

136
00:10:50,590 --> 00:10:54,950
The rest is up to you... Natsu...

137
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,820
This is...

138
00:11:37,770 --> 00:11:41,140
Much blood has been spilled.

139
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:43,580
Children's blood.

140
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:50,140
Because of their parent's failure, the 
children have suffered and shed tears.

141
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:56,650
Enough of this, you and I.

142
00:11:59,540 --> 00:12:01,650
We must put this to an end!

143
00:12:05,970 --> 00:12:07,440
Master!

144
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:18,940
You wish to cause a disaster?

145
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:29,010
If it's for the sake of my guild!

146
00:12:57,910 --> 00:13:03,180
The wood... The land... The 
sky... They are frightened.

147
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,090
This is why...

148
00:13:07,090 --> 00:13:08,840
...I hate humans!

149
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:13,270
Such foolish creatures, always 
spinning tales of battle!

150
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:15,390
Makarov, you fool!

151
00:13:15,390 --> 00:13:18,250
If you want to die so bad, 
just croak on your own!

152
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,530
Mystogan...

153
00:13:31,230 --> 00:13:32,370
May I have one?

154
00:13:33,490 --> 00:13:35,020
Ah, I see.

155
00:13:35,020 --> 00:13:39,180
I had thought it odd how quickly 
Makarov was able to recover.

156
00:13:39,770 --> 00:13:43,280
So it was you who went and collected 
Makarov's magical power, yes?

157
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,830
I never said you could have it!

158
00:13:47,620 --> 00:13:50,370
The war will soon be over.

159
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:55,950
I don't want to say anything 
to encourage more human war,

160
00:13:55,950 --> 00:13:58,500
but you're one of Makarov's friends, right?

161
00:13:58,500 --> 00:14:00,000
You should leave here and go...

162
00:14:00,370 --> 00:14:02,480
You've been off fighting 
on your own, haven't you?

163
00:14:12,460 --> 00:14:14,040
Phantom's flags?

164
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:19,430
Wait... Did he go around crushing each 
of Phantom's branches on his own?

165
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:25,430
May I have another apple?

166
00:14:25,430 --> 00:14:28,600
You'd better pick up this 
trash before you leave.

167
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:32,240
Really...

168
00:14:33,730 --> 00:14:36,350
I've given up on you people.

169
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:40,230
Such power can only give birth to sadness.

170
00:14:40,230 --> 00:14:46,220
And inside the fierce maelstrom, the 
rage makes one forget the sadness.

171
00:14:50,590 --> 00:14:55,240
I wish to believe in a righteous light 
that encompasses the rage and sadness...

172
00:14:56,140 --> 00:15:00,250
The righteous light which guides all things.

173
00:15:18,450 --> 00:15:23,450
What is this warm, familiar magical power?

174
00:15:32,570 --> 00:15:34,950
Everyone get away from here!

175
00:15:36,010 --> 00:15:37,000
Master!

176
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,380
Why is he here?

177
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:40,040
Do as he says!

178
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:44,790
Let's go.

179
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:46,270
But...

180
00:15:46,270 --> 00:15:47,910
Nee-chan, can you stand?

181
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:52,430
Now that you are here, I have 
no need for the small-fry.

182
00:15:52,430 --> 00:15:55,950
Don't worry, I'll finish 
them off later, of course.

183
00:15:55,950 --> 00:15:59,010
We'll only get in his way by being here.

184
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:01,620
Leave everything to the master!

185
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:08,840
It's been 6 years since we've 
last faced each other, hasn't it?

186
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:14,560
And Fairy Tail has grown 
so much in that time.

187
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:17,120
But it's been destroyed now, hasn't it?

188
00:16:17,700 --> 00:16:22,300
A guild is not a building. 
It's a union between people!

189
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:25,300
But I'm so happy.

190
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:30,880
I get to establish the order of 
superiority among the wizard saints

191
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:34,880
I really owe everything to my 
kids! You've all done well.

192
00:16:35,590 --> 00:16:38,850
Be proud to be part of Fairy Tail!

193
00:16:45,130 --> 00:16:46,000
What the...

194
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:46,730
The sky!

195
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:48,060
Watch it!

196
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:50,040
The ground is...

197
00:16:50,040 --> 00:16:50,640
An earthquake?

198
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:51,900
What the heck's going on?

199
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:04,330
Dead Wave!

200
00:17:29,150 --> 00:17:30,180
Natsu!

201
00:17:30,180 --> 00:17:31,340
Are you okay?

202
00:17:32,010 --> 00:17:33,940
But what was that?

203
00:17:36,030 --> 00:17:39,200
This is Gramps' magic, no doubt about it!

204
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:47,210
Impressive.

205
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:50,790
Such magical power, and yet so young.

206
00:17:50,790 --> 00:17:54,550
You do have what it takes to 
bear the title of Wizard Saint.

207
00:17:55,610 --> 00:18:01,460
If you had used that power for good and became
a role-model for the younger generation,

208
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:06,050
you would have led the
magic world to its future...

209
00:18:07,060 --> 00:18:09,840
You're lecturing me, aren't you?

210
00:18:09,840 --> 00:18:17,490
As is Fairy Tail tradition, I shall count 
to three before rendering judgment upon you.

211
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:21,530
Beg for mercy.

212
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:27,750
One!

213
00:18:28,450 --> 00:18:31,000
I wondered what you'd say. But this?

214
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,550
"Beg for mercy?!"

215
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:35,580
Two!

216
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:40,130
You expect the number-one guild 
in the country to bow down to <i>you</i>?

217
00:18:40,130 --> 00:18:41,710
Don't kid yourself!

218
00:18:41,710 --> 00:18:44,020
I can fight toe-to-toe with you!

219
00:18:44,020 --> 00:18:47,600
No, I won't hold back, so 
I'm actually more powerful!

220
00:18:47,840 --> 00:18:49,560
Three!

221
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:52,610
You're the one who should beg for mercy!

222
00:18:52,610 --> 00:18:53,600
Begone!

223
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:58,360
Disappear with your brats into 
the ranks of history, Fairy Tail!

224
00:18:58,360 --> 00:19:00,610
Time's up!

225
00:19:01,320 --> 00:19:04,960
Die, Fairy Tail!

226
00:19:13,340 --> 00:19:16,920
Fairy Law is invoked!

227
00:19:34,100 --> 00:19:36,420
What is this light?

228
00:19:36,420 --> 00:19:37,820
So bright...

229
00:19:39,810 --> 00:19:41,150
The shades are...

230
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,570
Only they are disappearing.

231
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:46,230
One after another!

232
00:19:46,230 --> 00:19:48,010
But nothing's happening to us!

233
00:19:48,010 --> 00:19:50,200
This light... is compassionate.

234
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:52,350
It's Fairy Law.

235
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:54,620
Fairy Law?

236
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:58,500
Righteous light that slays the darkness.

237
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:02,070
It slays only that which the 
caster believes is the enemy.

238
00:20:02,420 --> 00:20:08,380
It's a super-powerful magic, 
now counted as legend.

239
00:20:35,870 --> 00:20:39,140
Never come near Fairy Tail again.

240
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:44,240
The council will not stay silent 
after things have gotten so flashy.

241
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:47,330
You should watch out for 
your own skin for a while.

242
00:20:47,330 --> 00:20:49,210
And same for me...

243
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:53,430
The sadness...

244
00:20:54,390 --> 00:20:56,790
He's wide open, just like the last time!

245
00:20:56,790 --> 00:20:58,270
He's mine!

246
00:21:06,690 --> 00:21:10,990
It's over! The battle of 
the guilds is finished.

247
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:18,350
But if you try anything more, I'll "clean 
you out," and leave not a trace...

248
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:23,340
Take Jose with you and go home! Right now!

249
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:28,560
Yipee! We beat Phantom!

250
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:04,710
This victory is not from just my power,

251
00:22:06,430 --> 00:22:09,470
but a victory for our whole family.

252
00:22:16,540 --> 00:22:19,410
I knew you could do it, Gramps...

253
00:23:56,380 --> 00:24:00,720
Oh yeah, so why did Jose grab Lucy anyway?

254
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:05,090
Dunno. He had a kind of 
dirty look on his face...

255
00:24:05,090 --> 00:24:07,540
Maybe he had the hots for her or something?

256
00:24:07,540 --> 00:24:09,580
There are people in the world with 
freaky tastes like that, I guess.

257
00:24:09,580 --> 00:24:11,370
Who'd be interested in Lucy, after all?

258
00:24:11,370 --> 00:24:14,230
Well there's Loke, that's one at least.

259
00:24:14,230 --> 00:24:16,550
Next time: My Resolve!

260
00:24:16,850 --> 00:24:20,140
I'm worried about Lucy's future.

261
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:21,770
You're worried now? She's a lost cause...

262
00:24:22,030 --> 00:24:25,040
Natsu, you're cold as ice.

